snippet.title: Atari 2600 - Astroblast © 1982 Mattel - Gameplay
snippet.description: Shoot down a variety of fast-moving targets: falling meteors, spinning bombs, guided missiles - even a bomb-dropping UFO! The computer keeps score, and gives you more challenging game action the higher you go!
